  "title": "Sales Executive (HORECA)",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>This role is ideal for candidates who are motivated, eager to learn, and passionate about building relationships and driving business growth. You will be trained to use a consultative sales approach to identify customer needs, qualify leads, and develop sales opportunities with both new and existing clients.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Work towards achieving and exceeding assigned sales targets</li><li>Identify and develop new business opportunities while maintaining existing customer relationships</li><li>Learn to support and participate in sales discussions and negotiations with customers</li><li>Build strong rapport and long-term relationships with clients through effective communication and follow-up</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications & Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Fresh graduates are welcome to apply</strong></li><li>Prior internship, part-time, or project experience in sales, business development, or customer-facing roles is an advantage but not required</li><li>Basic knowledge of CRM systems or willingness to learn</li><li>Strong written and verbal communication skills</li><li>Self-motivated, positive attitude, and eager to grow in a sales career</li></ul>",
